                                            jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                                            sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/text/v2/text"
                                            text="&lt;p>Hear about how the clinical trials landscape has evolved over the last 10 years from our Australia and New Zealand Director of Clinical Operations, Shruti Chaturvedi.&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;/content/abbvie-com2/nz/en/who-we-are/our-stories/10-years-of-clinical-trials.html&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>Read more&lt;/a>&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>For more information about clinical trials in Australia, including AbbVie specific trials please visit:&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.australianclinicaltrials.gov.au/&quot;>https://www.australianclinicaltrials.gov.au/&lt;/a>&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;"
